title: High Fantasy Resource Bundle - RPGMaker
description:
This Resource Pack contains a collection of Western-styled fantasy resources. This Add-on Pack is compatible with the full version of "RPG MAKER VX, and RPG Maker VX Ace" and can be used with RPG Maker XP and IG Maker to create your own game.

This bundle ontains:
~ 70 Battle Backgrounds
~ 96 Front-View Battlers
~ 90 Side-View Battlers (may require a 3rd party script to utilize)
~ Over 200 Character Sprite Sheets!
~ 168 Faces (21 full sets)!
~ 6 Overlays for clouds and rain (may require a 3rd party script to utilize)
~ 35 Tile Sheets (9 auto-tile sheets, 26 B-E sheets)


Screenshots & more info: [url] http://www.rpgmakerweb.com/products/resource-packs/high-fantasy-resource-pack [/url]
